cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with image situation recognition using recurrent neural networks, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of RNNs, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with predicting noun entities, which involves NLP techniques and can be categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper involves transfer learning, which can be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
